OL,5,CSunak
OL,7,FA man has been given a suspended
OL,8,Fprison sentence for sending racist
OL,9,Fdeath threats to former prime minister
OL,10,FRishi Sunak.
OL,12,FLiam Shaw, 21, of Birkenhead, sent two
OL,13,Fthreatening and offensive emails to
OL,14,Fthe public email address of Mr Sunak
OL,15,Fon June 15 last year when the former
OL,16,FConservative leader was still prime
OL,17,Fminister, the Crown Prosecution
OL,18,FService (CPS) said.
