OL,5,CSunak
OL,7,FThe emails were spotted by Mr Sunak's
OL,8,Fpersonal assistant and reported to the
OL,9,Fpolice.
OL,11,FThe CPS said the language in the two
OL,12,Femails was "racist, offensive and
OL,13,Fsuggested Mr Sunak should be killed by
OL,14,Fthe public".
OL,16,FThe emails had been sent by Shaw's
OL,17,Fphone and police traced them to his
OL,18,Femail address and a hostel where he
OL,19,Fwas staying in Birkenhead, Merseyside.
