OL,7,FShaw was arrested by police on
OL,8,FSeptember 3 2024 and charged with two
OL,9,Fcounts of sending by a public
OL,10,Fcommunication network an offensive,
OL,11,Findecent, obscene, or menacing message.
OL,13,FWhen the allegations were put to him
OL,14,Fby police, Shaw said: "I don't even
OL,15,Fremember sending an email. I was
OL,16,Fprobably drunk."
OL,18,FShaw pleaded guilty to both counts at
OL,19,FLiverpool Magistrates' Court on July
OL,20,F10 2025.
