OL,7,FHe was sentenced at the same court on
OL,8,FWednesday to 14 weeks' imprisonment
OL,9,Ffor both counts, to run concurrently,
OL,10,Fwith the sentence suspended for 12
OL,11,Fmonths.
OL,13,FShaw must also complete 20 days of a
OL,14,Frehabilitation activity and a six-
OL,15,Fmonth drug rehabilitation course.
