OL,7,FThe CPS also successfully applied for
OL,8,Fa restraining order which the court
OL,9,Fimposed for two years ` it states that
OL,10,FShaw must have no contact with Mr
OL,11,FSunak or his constituency office in
OL,12,Fthat time.
OL,14,FDistrict Judge Timothy Boswell said at
OL,15,Fthe sentencing: "Direct access to your
OL,16,Fconstituency MP is a cornerstone of
OL,17,Fdemocracy. Misusing that access is
OL,18,Fdetrimental to the democratic process.
OL,19,FClearly it is a highly aggravating
OL,20,Ffactor for the offence."
