OL,7,FSenior Crown prosecutor Matthew Dixon,
OL,8,Fof CPS Mersey Cheshire, said: "Liam
OL,9,FShaw took to his phone that night to
OL,10,Fsend racist and threatening messages
OL,11,Fto a person in an extremely important
OL,12,Fpublic office.
OL,14,F"The work of Members of Parliament is
OL,15,Fextremely important and the police and
OL,16,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service play
OL,17,Ftheir part in keeping them safe and
OL,18,Fable to do their work without fear.
