OL,7,F"The Crown Prosecution Service has
OL,8,Falways and will continue to safeguard
OL,9,Fa person's right to freedom of
OL,10,Fexpression.
OL,12,F"But this is clearly a case where the
OL,13,Fcomments made were utterly beyond the
OL,14,Fboundary of what is tolerable in a
OL,15,Ffair, just and multi-racial society,
OL,16,Fand passed into the realm of
OL,17,Fcriminality.
OL,19,F"Racist abuse has no place, anywhere,
OL,20,Fin this day and age."
